caption.p: Sandwich ELISA assay for IL-6 (A, C) and IL-8 expression (B, D) after 24 h treatment of HIEC-6 (A, B) and PHH (C, D) with inhibitors MI-1900 or with MI-1907 at 50 µM. The data show the mean IL-6 and IL-8 concentrations (pg/mL ± SDs). None of the inhibitors increased IL-6 and IL-8 concentrations after 24 h treatment ( p>.05, n = 8).
